{"tid":2461432,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"認真介紹　手機俠　五大看點","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:21:55.000Z","uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f2dded7ddd979552e8341c020850c7fe7e1b47","tid":2461432,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"相信好多朋友都對「手機俠」三個字唔陌生，到底呢套係一套咩類型既作品呢？我地一齊黎探討下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《帶著智慧型手機闖蕩異世界。》是冬原パトラ所作的日本輕小說作品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSWWujjnzLzPgeaTvnEdokBHnuD6swfGKcpx8w7SP4p6o?filename=5s2P3ZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s2P3ZQ.jpg&h=006dfa7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcm263Hg4uciQsNyWAkvjEQ71cG9raemZ48duDPnmaq5R?filename=d96UwxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd96UwxC.jpg&h=4a228b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機俠精華！十分鐘看完上半季！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XLSxmogDdns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXLSxmogDdns&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=1d621067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XLSxmogDdns</a><br />\n（如果覺得太長可以set做兩倍速度，手機俠精華！５分半鐘看完上半季！）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❶作品核心設定：魔法設計、廣闊世界觀、經典ＡＣＧ元素</strong></span><br />\n魔法分為　六種屬性魔法　和　無屬性魔法<br />\n七種屬性　為　水、火、土、風、光、暗<br />\n<br />\n屬性魔法係借助世界的自然力量所施放，而無屬性魔法則偏向個人。<br />\n<br />\n屬性魔法唔係個個人都用得，要睇天份，天生的。所以本身就有三種屬性相性既人已經係嬴在起跑線。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">手機俠既設定可以套用至任何作品！萌王既惡魔召喚，骨王的不死族生成，都係屬暗屬性魔法。雷切／千鳥呢啲空氣震動就係風屬性魔法。黑色五葉草世界樹魔法就係土屬性魔法。\n記憶操作，物質變更（黑色五葉草格雷），呢啲非自然力量既現象控制，就係無屬性魔法。\n\n無屬性魔法係唔同既作品都有出現。《Re:Zero》既加護就係常駐型無屬性魔法，每個人唔同，天生。萊因哈魯特就係當中既最強。不過因為手機俠個世界魔法層次未去到咁高，所以冇加護既設定。\n另一套講無屬性魔法既作品就係《葬送的芙莉蓮》。無屬性魔法學唔到只係人既資質問題。當然仲係因為量好大。\n（火系既話你識入門就可以自己develop落去，精通哂成個火系魔法，無屬性魔法唔得）\n芙莉蓮一路旅行學習既大多都係無屬性魔法。例如捕鳥魔法。\n至於點解《七龍珠》入面孫悟空要三年先學識學瞬間移動，因為係無屬性魔法黎。\n《平職》入面七大神代魔法都係無屬性魔法。\n萌王既神之怒就係水+光既複合魔法。無心者就係暗魔法。\n</code></pre><br />\n（注１：呢套作品未有「氣」、「武技」等元素。）<br />\n（注２：呢套作品未有無詠唱既出現。雖然手機功用上有啲似）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kQ1GlO5grI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7kQ1GlO5grI&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=e9eefc15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7kQ1GlO5grI</a><br />\n透明魔法「invisible」同harry potter一樣，只係改變光線，唔能夠消聲。<br />\n結界可以封鎖針對空間既魔法，但封鎖唔到針對人類五感既魔法。<br />\n透明魔法「invisible」屬光屬性魔法，原因係佢係控制自然界既光。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左魔法，仲有過去、未來、東方、西方等等既設定。<br />\n當然仲有其他穿越者。<br />\n<br />\n日本：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTv4K2RA2gGQKSQyMUYnRWbDVimBQYLwH92kE51vbK5Dx?filename=xZdPkdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZdPkdN.jpg&h=f8283d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR7DdKkAEu595tbKM6SsgpSkUY1ZMygmfRreFAjBRooF7?filename=UxaYX0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxaYX0K.png&h=2b7dadcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科幻及現代科技：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSckC7anv4LwrR2rT3V4mocd2AEjjqyvbHouU2fCnYWMc?filename=7fyr6yB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fyr6yB.jpg&h=784b4d19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmegYbqbkDHUsAF1iuXcvTPkMHD7ATKLPLgpEFVVZA2BZM?filename=vxSXtQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxSXtQq.jpg&h=d40db686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX4XoMwRWfbuSNM8XtJtPSgiYvS5XuFNGxkX2Vzb3NEut?filename=80LaO7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80LaO7Z.jpg&h=8f7caec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVDn9wKD1U7UcBve4pE6ngiWFKZ5bnyE594zzjJUgoq9i?filename=qtt38Nj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqtt38Nj.jpg&h=e208c145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劍與魔法世界的ＲＰＧ屠龍：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcTEovuXbecyfcYhEYmUuL7QdfLsdiKF7aornaNdoKHd2?filename=R5jffv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5jffv6.jpg&h=ef6ba954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWqEuFBjXUwFCmzCPCyRB27t5jmf7UW9kogVhtPXVbKVm?filename=YV4iX1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYV4iX1Y.png&h=ed473fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n史萊姆／觸手：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYdxcVFLHsg3WSFSwWNji5heDqyERS3txBwBNsi1DFFe1?filename=x2PShGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2PShGq.jpg&h=2eb31ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYKp37St6egVjRFirEMsnhwDGqvNSrQuTMm1sQD7pQTTj?filename=18swyeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18swyeL.jpg&h=d84a8637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfV6MvNyUezdUTH63mqHqnQdd71XJQrMBJaJtc5eD5kDM?filename=f3pKTeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3pKTeL.jpg&h=9208db82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY96SaneuscAK74EWjdViAhLa35Nr3DCeggcrRJ78NuuX?filename=NnEnFgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnEnFgf.jpg&h=3cc98f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n奶油犬：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW21ePB9PxgunwknLwKjJXmenhQ9RNxRPJL1sx7DKgAf1?filename=GzVaOP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzVaOP0.jpg&h=2b530b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泳衣＆褔利：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRK6WCmBpk6WgnujLvPUV2bFFK4DrZsa5aXL7Z7ZU29YG?filename=41aaO3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41aaO3j.jpg&h=26a03e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUzjxvtb4s7DRyzwHisWFA86ctXvjafYzL7jicfsDo5Ke?filename=7Pvuj6C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Pvuj6C.gif&h=8303dedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPHqUpssGspegmCX4e7Zhk3oFidTC3Zv5bRL79G2rVBrT?filename=WcCc2jY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcCc2jY.gif&h=ac7ac6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXy6s1W7P9ionfjgAZ1qjAKFLZcSPfLnuAyxoSc9pJocc?filename=EmichTi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmichTi.gif&h=ee4e5fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfGvC1rrPLzvaYvsPWGCzKuetUA4hgqzSgWRoNyQXFNtU?filename=kyc1bbO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkyc1bbO.gif&h=23fa7032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他穿越者：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3euY31WHVB9Lw1kAWh3uAKJ1EJk4gh45afXvHTg4UkB?filename=nLp66LQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLp66LQ.jpg&h=159db7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❷由神明所致的死亡穿越</strong></span><br />\n因為本身就係神明做錯事，唔係主角強出頭被人吉死，或者俾卡車撞死，所以神明對住佢都好低聲下氣。但係主角實在太看破紅塵，令神明好驚訝。<br />\n因為主角實在太好人，唔止俾佢用手機，仲幫佢開掛。同其他作品唔同，無任何力量限制，要求等等，唔洗打魔王，唔洗做勇者，唔洗拜神。<br />\n因為呢個設定，故事發展可以有無限可能性。同類型無限伸延的作品有：《異世界迷宮黑心企業》（迷宮ブラックカンパニー）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbYdQcR2cYeskuH29Y9bbbCvv8pEqXR2RYEfueipERnRm?filename=qrqBKES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrqBKES.png&h=9dd604b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbuyj6GgmxZ4xZYjPcyokdaAQATp7oLTVBLfEAKujm8CZ?filename=0oUnFbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oUnFbV.jpg&h=03e94ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUS4TURFEkK74s9smj3zgYnr3VQ2H7pFqSKjZXrRAUn6U?filename=pEZ66Sn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEZ66Sn.jpg&h=e2b32b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmaqf9MZxbXu6qW9aJwg67ZkHdRBVvkp569bmsQXhmAMKM?filename=50X8ALQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50X8ALQ.jpg&h=053e9a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❸Slip</strong></span><br />\n愈簡單既魔法愈有效。對比起同類型作品，往往都要推陳出新，但係呢套只係用一招就可以由頭嬴到落尾。Slip係冇任何對抗手段，所有防衛魔法都失效。<br />\n有啲似一拳超人，簡單直接唔會輸。<br />\n當然無屬性魔法本身唔係攻擊用，仲要配合其他魔法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbcMKXjoyZxkASVEjbt92yrCMCURWXL6UYD1jFDB8AbnY?filename=cZ1EHvt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ1EHvt.jpg&h=988ae2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRPChAM1b835bPhJtiHJxLtu3nHwQECbTmNXQ6U1hwgcj?filename=Mf2sRck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf2sRck.jpg&h=c7b7fd61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>❹豐富人設</strong></span><br />\n人物設定十分豐富，各種屬性都有。<br />\n姊妹：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme7CWfdSd7TACSGxGP7dp2fSy9AcWKxeWFiX2qgToDQjf?filename=rbivONF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbivONF.jpg&h=056f2dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW3VifCb2dqkCWjVuTT6DvvKPtrKrD1mqY4t6gueDmwmV?filename=uBqBKCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBqBKCZ.jpg&h=92cb0c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真宮寺櫻／博麗靈夢：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP75NkeSvNmDDZvTB4mxat52bibxwSnFdGSnj2V7kU5nL?filename=U6DS2eu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6DS2eu.png&h=606c1574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNVegz7LjtsnFrAtEGiogt8Z49LUeBC2U3wZYJ81JsMdc?filename=R9q94sP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9q94sP.png&h=7f72c2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX6rNNHa2hH66dEVLLydsCrVxkXydGvcZPF2ytFyouk1q?filename=094rnuc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F094rnuc.jpg&h=e49be4e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n異色瞳：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdaUMatWyCTxLQBGo1c1zW2YEu2ypkWyqCh2Bu54qexrG?filename=gryDdho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgryDdho.jpg&h=8f08bc57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQhJjyQgxpxasPMVLMEwfNwURpo4AraAKJekZDf6w8c1Y?filename=55kuj4i.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55kuj4i.gif&h=a546c935&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幼女：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWMPPEas91gzRS1EHZQ2FqGyB7trPiYp2BQtMoNiV1vyY?filename=Z8JS2k0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8JS2k0.jpg&h=f10d6129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTYSfhqt24gBVuXAnJNhLBqLZqXhRA13w9rSNi9Z3Stoo?filename=N4bEHoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4bEHoK.jpg&h=016a01b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nＢＢＡ：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd6tgHjtGUvALWq8Ant6rehKUFEiNrVi4KFrG7KFMjyRc?filename=rzz66Av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frzz66Av.jpg&h=168d4c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ79t1gvB3Grmceua3sPB3P5EAwipuB4YP686WYqWDmA5?filename=gtdWKnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtdWKnE.jpg&h=2fb4721b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQuZqSPs5bpRVK3o6MN8ABfvxiZDsQwWeDWKWJXvUnF9Y?filename=pR5qCUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpR5qCUe.jpg&h=b0625fc5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nＡＩ機械人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV2mgE8jict5XQNPszdKexTLSvNV8tS3N8Tg43grXgeX8?filename=oJxMnhh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJxMnhh.png&h=61b97f07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVs2FYLJBh98VfGWFGMQkrRGiYbPsyPQbNCFsaHtfUVH5?filename=e2bUwdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2bUwdu.jpg&h=06cf5fb4&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n雷姆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbh5wkbS2qhnMxdCr81HZTcwPZEVfcbqFpJyQqq5Y7WWV?filename=90WhtP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90WhtP4.jpg&h=79c41fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n御姐：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTeymFx1SjNdJmKJuPLHagkztx5XsWq6LY3E6HyVRsvzu?filename=7fqJ856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fqJ856.jpg&h=e29bce74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSqTwkAt8M5QaxseBgrzACv3zZB1tsFjqkx1uoQKPH3GD?filename=BsyPj9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsyPj9C.jpg&h=d04fd6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>❺萌寵</strong></span><br />\n迫拉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTxJG9RyggRYqFjp8g96eLck6CMYY7eMWPuUG2EA5kam2?filename=h2m5CHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2m5CHe.jpg&h=ea134478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUqnTE2ZvCsmCZb3bHDK5hSzyue98piAD2EG9kfvvqw7k?filename=SfKffGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfKffGP.jpg&h=6a7ef9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琥珀（白虎）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRJCaVvozJDGKAG42MWxRuBf27nrEGJULm7cCv4UPJuk3?filename=2w7gKqn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i